🔐 AUTH FLOW (Frontend)
User opens app
     ↓
Check auth state (Redux / Context / storage)
     ↓
NOT LOGGED IN → Redirect to Login Page
     ↓
Login Form (UI)
     ↓
User enters credentials / OTP
     ↓
useAuth hook
     ↓
authService (API call)
     ↓
JWT stored (cookie/localStorage)
     ↓
Global state updated
     ↓
Redirect to Dashboard (role-based)

🏢 COMPANY + VENDOR FLOW (Frontend)
Admin Dashboard (UI)
     ↓
Company Management Page
     ↓
Create Company (Form → Service → API)
     ↓
Vendor registers (Public UI)
     ↓
Admin Approval Page
     ↓
Approve button (UI)
     ↓
useAdmin hook → adminService
     ↓
UI updates (Approved status)

🛍️ PRODUCT FLOW (Frontend)
Admin/Vendor Dashboard
     ↓
Product Form Page
     ↓
Fill Product Details (UI)
     ↓
Variant + Pricing + Category
     ↓
useProduct hook
     ↓
productService → API
     ↓
Success → UI refresh

User Side:
     ↓
Search Page / Product Page
     ↓
Fetch products (useProduct)
     ↓
Render catalog (UI)

🛒 BUYING FLOW (Frontend)
User browses products
     ↓
Clicks "Add to Cart"
     ↓
Cart State Updated (Redux / Hook)
     ↓
Cart Page UI
     ↓
Checkout button
     ↓
Order creation API (useOrder)
     ↓
Order success → Navigate to Payment

💳 PAYMENT FLOW (Frontend)
Order Page
     ↓
Click "Pay Now"
     ↓
PaymentPage UI
     ↓
paymentService → initiate API
     ↓
Redirect / Open Gateway (Razorpay/Stripe)

Success:
     ↓
Verify Payment API
     ↓
Update UI → Success screen

OR

Credit Flow:
     ↓
Select "Use Credit"
     ↓
creditService → API
     ↓
Ledger updated → UI refreshed

🚚 LOGISTICS FLOW (Frontend)
Order Placed
     ↓
Delivery Page
     ↓
useDelivery hook
     ↓
deliveryService → API
     ↓
Render RouteMap (UI)

Status Updates:
     ↓
Pending → Shipped → Delivered
     ↓
UI updates dynamically

📄 INVOICE FLOW (Frontend)
Order Success
     ↓
Navigate to Invoice Page
     ↓
useInvoice hook
     ↓
invoiceService → API
     ↓
Render InvoicePreview (UI)
     ↓
Download / Print (future)

🔔 NOTIFICATION FLOW (Frontend)
User logged in
     ↓
NotificationPage loads
     ↓
useNotification hook
     ↓
notificationService → API

User action:
     ↓
Click notification
     ↓
markAsRead()
     ↓
UI updates instantly

📊 ANALYTICS FLOW (Frontend)
Dashboard Page
     ↓
Filters selected (date range)
     ↓
useAnalytics hook
     ↓
analyticsService → API
     ↓
Render KPI Widgets + Charts